data:
"You tell me whar a man gits his corn pone, en I'll tell you what his 'pinions is."

Part of this means our incentives shape our constraints. (there is more too it - Twain also says all opinions originate in this way. See: [https://paulgraham.com/cornpone.html](https://paulgraham.com/cornpone.html)
for a more complete excerpt)
